          <div class="h-8 w-24 bg-gray-300 rounded-full opacity-50 shrink-0"></div>
          <div class="h-8 w-24 bg-gray-300 rounded-full opacity-50 shrink-0"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: PHILOSOPHY -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 pb-24 pt-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-text leading-tight">
          Design is not just what it looks like. It's how it works and scales.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <p class="text-lg text-grey leading-relaxed">
          I believe that minimalism is the ultimate sophistication. In an era of digital noise, clarity is the most powerful tool a brand can possess. My approach removes the unnecessary to amplify what truly matters.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-grey leading-relaxed">
          Every project begins with a deep dive into the business logic. We don't just "make things pretty"; we architect systems that drive conversion, retention, and brand loyalty.
        </p>
        <div>
          <a href="/about.html" class="text-primary font-medium hover:underline inline-flex items-center gap-1 mt-2">Read about my mission &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: WHY WORK WITH ME -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 pb-24 pt-12">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-text mb-4">
        Why Work With Me
      </h2>
      <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-primary mb-8"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-cardborder rounded-card p-8 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-sm">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-primary">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl mb-3 text-text">Three disciplines. One person.</h3>
        <p class="text-grey leading-relaxed text-sm">Eliminating handoff chaos by integrating research, design, and automation into a single, cohesive workflow. Faster iterations, zero friction.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-cardborder rounded-card p-8 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-sm">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-primary">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl mb-3 text-text">Direct Access</h3>
        <p class="text-grey leading-relaxed text-sm">Skip the account managers and sales reps. You work directly with the expert responsible for every pixel and line of code in your project.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-cardborder rounded-card p-8 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-sm">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-primary">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 12l3-3 3 3 4-4M8 21l4-4 4 4M3 4h18M4 4h16v12a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V4z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl mb-3 text-text">Measured Outcomes</h3>
        <p class="text-grey leading-relaxed text-sm">Every automation and interface is backed by rigorous UX research to ensure measurable business growth and tangible user satisfaction.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: EXPERTISE -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 pb-24 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-text mb-4">
        Three disciplines. One person.<br>
        <span class="text-teal">No handoff chaos.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-grey leading-relaxed">
        Traditional agencies lose context between research and implementation. I own the entire lifecycle of a problem.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
